Maintainer: Youngsun Kim <yskstat@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools for the easy implementation of 
    Structural Latent Class Models (SLCM) encompassing 
    Latent Transition Analysis (LTA), latent class profile analysis (LCPA), 
    joint latent class analysis (JLCA), and additional extended models involving 
    multiple latent class variables.
